dy nearly sold him as a young horse because she found him boring, only stopping short of doing so on the advice of her sister Hannah.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 2112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The emergence\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"Moody\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"'Bomber\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"the great entertainers\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"Moody\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1981}, {\"ngram\": \"a young horse\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2014}, {\"ngram\": \"the advice\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"her sister\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"Hannah\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their story is exactly the kind of salve required torebuild the ancient discipline's reputation.\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2210, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their story\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly the kind\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"salve\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"the ancient discipline's reputation\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was expecting a lovely 10-day holiday in France but this is quite a bit better in reality,\\\" joked Moody.\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2256, \"end\": 2262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8836113941186104, \"rank\": 0.05164125494714328, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lovely 10-day holiday\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"reality\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2304}, {\"ngram\": \"Moody\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I did not have the pressure for a long period beforehand,