lled Norman, we all called him 'Bomb' for some reason.\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2880, \"end\": 2886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy\", \"score\": 0.9999503534878111, \"rank\": 4.909572813210815e-05, \"text\": \"Norman\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normandy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bomb\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2911}, {\"ngram\": \"some reason\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, it was a little bit of a homage to him as well as the alcoholic beverage.\\\"\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 3008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"a homage\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 2965}, {\"ngram\": \"the alcoholic beverage\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 3006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aged 57, Hester became the second-oldest British Olympic medallist of the post-war era, with only fellow equestrian legend Nick Skelton having been older when he reached the podium.\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3019, \"end\": 3025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4830049788451544e-14, \"text\": \"Hester\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hester_Thrale\"}, {\"begin\": 3051, \"end\": 3058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.880095305690293, \"rank\": 0.1263075202507095, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3115, \"end\": 3125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9989113911269035, \"rank\": 0.0010897933188120307, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\